  "cooked_remote": "<p><strong>【标签】</strong> <code>社会服务</code>/<code>社会公益</code></p>\n<p><strong>【标题】</strong> 【社会服务赛道】心镜三维<span lang=\"EN-US\">——</span>正念<span lang=\"EN-US\">·</span>抑郁<span lang=\"EN-US\">·</span>自闭「三位一体」心理在线评估系统<span lang=\"EN-US\">Demo</span></p>\n<p><strong>【正文】</strong></p>\n<p><strong>0. 先和大家打个招呼吧 <img src=\"https://forum.trae.cn/images/emoji/twitter/waving_hand.png?v=15\" title=\":waving_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":waving_hand:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>你是谁：<strong>我是一名</strong>数字化转型咨询顾问</strong>。在此之前，我做了多年的程序员和系统架构师，后来转做解决方案架构师、产品经理，一直到现在帮企业做数字化转型咨询。可以说，我既写过底层代码，也画过架构图，还做过产品原型和战略规划。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>你是怎么用 TRAE 把 Demo 做出来的：</strong> 这次参赛，算是把「技术底子」和「对心理学的兴趣」第一次真正结合在了一起。虽然我有技术背景，但说实话，一个人从零搭建三套完整的评估系统，还要做前端、后端、数据库、部署<span lang=\"EN-US\">——</span>如果按传统方式，至少得折腾两三周。用<span lang=\"EN-US\">TRAE</span>之后，我把脑子里想的需求直接「讲」给它，它帮我生成了<span lang=\"EN-US\">80%</span>的代码和配置，我只需要聚焦在量表逻辑验证和产品体验打磨上。这种「想法直接变成产品」的效率，真的让我这个老程序员也感到惊喜。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>（我们相信，每个作品背后都有一个真实的人。这段不计入评分，但真诚的分享，会让你的作品更有温度、也更容易被看到 <img src=\"https://forum.trae.cn/images/emoji/twitter/sparkles.png?v=15\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>1. Demo 简介</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>是什么：一套基于<span lang=\"EN-US\">Web</span>的「三位一体」心理在线评估系统，用户通过浏览器即可完成专业心理量表测评、查看个性化报告、获得后续行动建议。（ 网站）；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>面向谁：长期受情绪困扰、希望进行自我筛查的成年人（白领、学生、宝妈）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> 、担忧孩子发育特征、需要早期判断是否就医的家长<span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span> 、心理咨询师、社工、学校辅导员等需要客观量表辅助初筛的从业者。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>主要功能：</p>\n</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"md-table\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>功能模块</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>正念灵活性评估</td>\n<td>基于 MAAS / DERS / RRS / VLQ 四大量表（53 题），评估正念觉察、情绪调节、反刍思维、价值生活四个维度</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>抑郁症在线评估</td>\n<td>基于 PHQ-9 / BDI-II / SDS / HAMD-17 / EPDS 五大量表（53 题），覆盖产后抑郁专项筛查</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>自闭症谱系评估</td>\n<td>基于 ABC（1.5–14 岁）/ AQ（16 岁+）双量表（107 题），支持儿童与成人双年龄段</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>统一账号体系</td>\n<td>三个系统共享一套注册登录账号，一次注册即可跨系统使用</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>个性化报告</td>\n<td>测评完成后生成多维度可视化报告，将分数翻译成可执行的下一步建议</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div><p>**(1)正念灵活性评估：**基于 MAAS / DERS / RRS / VLQ 四大量表（53 题），评估正念觉察、情绪调节、反刍思维、价值生活四个维度</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/f/c/fcda781c8d7ffde70d64386e37d3499ae15ee82d.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/A4QodyOUGWSB9AlSQOJabCMhV3n.png?dl=1\" title=\"Mindfulness-03\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/f/c/fcda781c8d7ffde70d64386e37d3499ae15ee82d_2_639x500.png\" alt=\"Mindfulness-03\" data-base62-sha1=\"A4QodyOUGWSB9AlSQOJabCMhV3n\" width=\"639\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/f/c/fcda781c8d7ffde70d64386e37d3499ae15ee82d_2_639x500.png, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/f/c/fcda781c8d7ffde70d64386e37d3499ae15ee82d_2_958x750.png 1.5x, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/f/c/fcda781c8d7ffde70d64386e37d3499ae15ee82d.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"F3F2EC\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Mindfulness-03</span><span class=\"informations\">1179×922 42.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>**(2)抑郁症在线评估：**基于 PHQ-9 / BDI-II / SDS / HAMD-17 / EPDS 五大量表（53 题），覆盖产后抑郁专项筛查</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/6/0/60b85833b70a4578eef321e3a955485b9a6fc03b.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/dNCNchekWLu6aBTF3tpX3H89rbd.png?dl=1\" title=\"depression-03\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/6/0/60b85833b70a4578eef321e3a955485b9a6fc03b_2_685x500.png\" alt=\"depression-03\" data-base62-sha1=\"dNCNchekWLu6aBTF3tpX3H89rbd\" width=\"685\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/6/0/60b85833b70a4578eef321e3a955485b9a6fc03b_2_685x500.png, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/6/0/60b85833b70a4578eef321e3a955485b9a6fc03b_2_1027x750.png 1.5x, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/6/0/60b85833b70a4578eef321e3a955485b9a6fc03b_2_1370x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"E5EAE8\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">depression-03</span><span class=\"informations\">1649×1203 90.1 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>**(3)自闭症谱系评估：**基于 ABC（1.5–14 岁）/ AQ（16 岁+）双量表（107 题），支持儿童与成人双年龄段</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/b/7/b75309e9d700f70a103b0ca34a2ec3758b7475a6.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/q9LhMdQ6yD2PLnqGDKaXjmDdHyS.png?dl=1\" title=\"Autism-03\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/b/7/b75309e9d700f70a103b0ca34a2ec3758b7475a6_2_650x499.png\" alt=\"Autism-03\" data-base62-sha1=\"q9LhMdQ6yD2PLnqGDKaXjmDdHyS\" width=\"650\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/b/7/b75309e9d700f70a103b0ca34a2ec3758b7475a6_2_650x499.png, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/b/7/b75309e9d700f70a103b0ca34a2ec3758b7475a6_2_975x748.png 1.5x, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/b/7/b75309e9d700f70a103b0ca34a2ec3758b7475a6_2_1300x998.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBEDDC\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Autism-03</span><span class=\"informations\">1583×1216 147 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>**(4)个性化报告：**测评完成后生成多维度可视化报告，将分数翻译成可执行的下一步建议</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/0/f/0f86ee427cff6ce50c512b9f5def43347c4746c0.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/2dmfu320COpAE0v4nRhViG7J9fO.png?dl=1\" title=\"Mindfulness-12\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/0/f/0f86ee427cff6ce50c512b9f5def43347c4746c0_2_652x500.png\" alt=\"Mindfulness-12\" data-base62-sha1=\"2dmfu320COpAE0v4nRhViG7J9fO\" width=\"652\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/0/f/0f86ee427cff6ce50c512b9f5def43347c4746c0_2_652x500.png, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/0/f/0f86ee427cff6ce50c512b9f5def43347c4746c0_2_978x750.png 1.5x, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/0/f/0f86ee427cff6ce50c512b9f5def43347c4746c0.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"F3F5F2\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Mindfulness-12</span><span class=\"informations\">1160×889 25.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/d/8/d8f4da1c66ea309f8e2184432aeabf92600e00f0.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/uXhJ32PANd2S4HCV9gQJ4jmcTVC.png?dl=1\" title=\"Mindfulness-18\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/d/8/d8f4da1c66ea309f8e2184432aeabf92600e00f0_2_444x500.png\" alt=\"Mindfulness-18\" data-base62-sha1=\"uXhJ32PANd2S4HCV9gQJ4jmcTVC\" width=\"444\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/d/8/d8f4da1c66ea309f8e2184432aeabf92600e00f0_2_444x500.png, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/d/8/d8f4da1c66ea309f8e2184432aeabf92600e00f0_2_666x750.png 1.5x, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/d/8/d8f4da1c66ea309f8e2184432aeabf92600e00f0.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"F0F2F1\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Mindfulness-18</span><span class=\"informations\">799×898 98.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>2. Demo 创作思路</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>灵感来源</strong>：身边越来越多朋友被职业倦怠、产后抑郁、孩子疑似谱系特质等问题困扰，去医院挂号要排队数周，市面上的小测试又像<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>星座娱乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>，缺少科学性与连贯性。我们希望把临床公认的量表，组合成一套<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>自己也能用<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>的体检式入口。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>想解决的问题：</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>公立医院心理科预约周期长、流程门槛高<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></li>\n<li>网络上的心理<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>测试<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>娱乐化严重，缺乏临床效度<span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></li>\n<li>各类量表分散在论文与<span lang=\"EN-US\">PDF</span>里，普通人不会选、读不懂、用不上 <span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></li>\n<li>单一维度评估容易误判，例如把谱系特质误读为社交焦 虑 <span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>**为什么做这个方向：**心理健康的早期筛查是一个真实存在且被忽视的需求。正念、抑郁、自闭三个领域看似独立，实则共享<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>觉察<span lang=\"EN-US\">—</span>调节<span lang=\"EN-US\">—</span>行动<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>的心理机制。将三者整合为<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>三位一体<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>系统，既能降低用户使用门槛，又能通过交叉维度提升评估准确性，具有明确的社会服务价值。。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>3. Demo 体验地址（三选一）</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>正念<span lang=\"EN-US\">·</span>抑郁<span lang=\"EN-US\">·</span>自闭「三位一体」心理在线评估系统</strong>，可通过邮箱注册后登录进行在线测试，<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>个系统共享一个注册账号:</p>\n</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"md-table\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Demo系统</th>\n<th>访问地址</th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>正念灵活性评估系统</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://mindfulness-care.space/mindfulness\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://mindfulness-care.space/mindfulness</a></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>抑郁症在线评估系统</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://mindfulness-care.space/depression\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://mindfulness-care.space/depression</a></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>自闭症谱系评估系统</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://mindfulness-care.space/autism\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://mindfulness-care.space/autism</a></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div><p><strong>4. TRAE 实践过程</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>清晰展示用 TRAE 完成 Demo 开发的完整流程；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>附<strong>开发关键步骤截图（不少于 3 张）：</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/0/3/032874b7fb8c4fbef62717bbc3ac604e506d5856.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/rW6KpcS76QZVxlQEw6XKtiPn8y.png?dl=1\" title=\"开发关键步骤截图-001\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/0/3/032874b7fb8c4fbef62717bbc3ac604e506d5856_2_690x377.png\" alt=\"开发关键步骤截图-001\" data-base62-sha1=\"rW6KpcS76QZVxlQEw6XKtiPn8y\" width=\"690\" height=\"377\" srcset=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/0/3/032874b7fb8c4fbef62717bbc3ac604e506d5856_2_690x377.png, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/0/3/032874b7fb8c4fbef62717bbc3ac604e506d5856_2_1035x565.png 1.5x, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/0/3/032874b7fb8c4fbef62717bbc3ac604e506d5856_2_1380x754.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"212224\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">开发关键步骤截图-001</span><span class=\"informations\">2560×1400 394 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/original/3X/8/b/8bbb385cf14899ced7f65e8b586d6bc144885913.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/jW7u7ev447c6Oy7dQPzYu8fLsb1.png?dl=1\" title=\"开发关键步骤截图-002\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/8/b/8bbb385cf14899ced7f65e8b586d6bc144885913_2_690x377.png\" alt=\"开发关键步骤截图-002\" data-base62-sha1=\"jW7u7ev447c6Oy7dQPzYu8fLsb1\" width=\"690\" height=\"377\" srcset=\"https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/8/b/8bbb385cf14899ced7f65e8b586d6bc144885913_2_690x377.png, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/8/b/8bbb385cf14899ced7f65e8b586d6bc144885913_2_1035x565.png 1.5x, https://trae-forum-cdn.trae.com.cn/prod/optimized/3X/8/b/8bbb385cf14899ced7f65e8b586d6bc144885913_2_1380x754.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"222325\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">开发关键步骤截图-002</span><span class=\"informations\">2560×1400 472 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href